OL,3,CTeenager campaigns for end to violence
OL,4,Cagainst women and girls
OL,6,FNiamh wants men and boys to help stamp
OL,7,Fout the problem by educating
OL,8,Fthemselves on the impact it can have.
OL,10,FShe said: "They need to want to learn.
OL,11,FThey need to want to help. Women are
OL,12,Ftalking to other women about how they
OL,13,Ffeel unsafe and men aren't really
OL,14,Flistening.
OL,16,F"It would be so useful if men would
OL,17,Fturn to each other and say actually
OL,18,Fthat's not okay, that would hurt a
OL,19,Fwoman's feelings or that's a really
OL,20,Fdangerous thing to say."
