OL,3,CTeenager campaigns for end to violence
OL,4,Cagainst women and girls
OL,6,Fshow a rise in reports of sexual
OL,7,Foffences and harassment against
OL,8,Fteenage girls on the rail network.
OL,10,FIn 2022, 663 teenage girls reported
OL,11,Fsexual offences or harassment to
OL,12,FBritish Transport Police.
OL,14,FIn 2023, this rose to 886 reports, at
OL,15,F25% increase.
OL,17,FThe 25% increase is thought to be
OL,18,Fpartly due to more teenagers reporting
OL,19,Fincidents but police believe that many
OL,20,Fgirls are staying silent.
