OL,3,CTeenager campaigns for end to violence
OL,4,Cagainst women and girls
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Nia Mellor, British
OL,7,FTransport Police, said: "Women and
OL,8,Fgirls don't think that they will be
OL,9,Fbelieved.
OL,11,F"They don't think that what they've
OL,12,Fexperienced is serious enough to
OL,13,Freport and for us we would say that
OL,14,Fnothing is too trivial, nothing is too
OL,15,Fsmall.
OL,17,F"Anything that makes you feel
OL,18,Funcomfortable on your journey, please
OL,19,Fdo report it to us."
