OL,6,FNiamh is now working on surveying
OL,7,Fschools across the region to find out
OL,8,Fthe impact sexual harassment is having
OL,9,Fon girls.
OL,11,FNiamh said: "Any person that speak up
OL,12,Fabout sexual assault and domestic
OL,13,Fviolence, it's really difficult.
OL,15,F"I think that if you come forward to
OL,16,Fthe police or even if you just mention
OL,17,Fit to a friend or family member,
OL,18,Fthat's really brave and you should be
OL,19,Fproud of yourself."
